<%@ taglib uri="/portletAPI" prefix="portletAPI" %>

<portletAPI:init/>

<b>Help</b>

This RSS portlet is a technology demosntration. It is not intended for real use.
<p/>

<b>View</b>       <br/>
The selected RSS feed will be displayed. The actual feeds will be refreshed (reloaded)
every 5 minutes.
<p>

<b>Edit</b>       <br/>
The user can select a defined RSS feed to display in <i>view</i> mode. Furthermore it is
possible to show the url of the selected feed.
<p>

<b>Configure</b><br/>
An admin define new rss feeds for the user. It is also possible to remove feeds.
